      <p>The first round of contextual advice was focussed on helping someone use their donation matching. If someone was making a donation we display how much matching would be available afterwards. By doing so, they could decide whether to change how much they’re giving.</p>
      <p>If someone was making a recurring donation, we show how much that person could give monthly to take advantage of their full year’s matching.</p>
